title: March Balloons Frank Lloyd Wright Earrings
description:
These earrings are adapted from a detail of Frank Lloyd Wright’s unrealized design for a LIBERTY magazine cover, "March Balloons” 1927. Frank Lloyd Wright (1867-1959) is considered the greatest architect of the 20th century. His legacy is one of America’s cultural treasures.

Details:

• Solid brass with gold finish

• Ear wires are gold plated

• Hangs approx. 1.85"
